Simple CRUD example for TDD (Test Driven Development) in Java.
The example uses Spring, Hibernate, JUnit and Concordion.

Procedure used:         
In springToolSuite, create a new Spring MVC project
In pom.xml, ensure latest versions used

Maven commands:
mvn clean compile test 
will compile and run all tests

mvn jetty:run
will start applicaton at http://localhost:8080 by default

Contact me at vijay_nathani@yahoo.com for any issues.
